1. Створення замовлення
POST /api/orders
Request:
{
  "user_id": 123,
  "cafe_id": 45,
  "items": [
    {"product_id": 10, "quantity": 1},
    {"product_id": 12, "quantity": 2}
  ],
  "payment_method": "card"
}

Response (201 Created):
{
  "order_id": 789,
  "status": "pending",
  "estimated_time": "5 min"
}

Errors:
400 - invalid request
402 - payment failed
404 - cafe not found
